<P>
<P>
In this exercise you will run the Client side of the Remote Object Serialization
project.

All of the files have been created for you.
<P>
In this exercise you will see how to use the Delegation Pattern to
allow a service to migrate.
This is covered
in the <A HREF="../../RMI.html#SerializingRemoteObjects">Serializing Remote Objects</A> 
section of the course notes.
</P>
